7. Clarity

   A really important point this one is (Yoda speak). Nothing is perhaps more
important than example that highlight or explain tricky parts of the rules. If
you want a guide on how *NOT* to use examples read ShadowRun.  Anything that
might be confusing should be explained in an example and an extended (read 4 or
5 pages at least, 8 or 9 would be better) sample of game play should be
included.

